00:47:09,340 --> 00:47:09,660
 znači,

1106
00:47:09,660 --> 00:47:10,840
 zaista trebamo

1107
00:47:10,840 --> 00:47:11,900
 oprit sve snage

1108
00:47:11,900 --> 00:47:13,120
 u post,

1109
00:47:13,120 --> 00:47:13,860
 u molitvu

1110
00:47:13,860 --> 00:47:15,180
 i kad nađu neke kušnje,

1111
00:47:15,180 --> 00:47:16,780
 udariti jače

1112
00:47:16,780 --> 00:47:17,300
 i jednostavno,

1113
00:47:17,300 --> 00:47:17,480
 evo,

1114
00:47:17,480 --> 00:47:18,580
 velim i bez posta

1115
00:47:18,580 --> 00:47:19,920
 teško se neke stvari

1116
00:47:19,920 --> 00:47:20,800
 pobjeđuju,

1117
00:47:20,800 --> 00:47:21,440
 evo nekako

1118
00:47:21,440 --> 00:47:23,880
